### Submit a registration application (public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "icPassportNumber": "A1234567",
  "address": "123 Rainforest Lane, Kuching, Sarawak",
  "reason": "I want to become a certified park guide",
  "cvS3Key": "cv/test-placeholder.pdf"
}

###

### List all registrations (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/registrations
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a single registration (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Approve a registration (admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "stationId": null
}

###

### Reject a registration (admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/registrations/{{registrationId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "reason": "Incomplete documentation provided"
}
